# Video Management: Edit and Delete for Circle Owners

This plan describes how to allow Circle Owners to edit and delete uploaded videos.

## Proposed Changes

### [Hook] useCircleVideos
#### [MODIFY] [useCircleVideos.ts](file:///c:/Users/elink/./.gemini/antigravity/scratch/MomNest/heart-lens-studio-main/src/hooks/useCircleVideos.ts)
- Add `deleteVideo` mutation:
  - Deletes the record from `circle_videos`.
  - Invalides `['circle-videos', circleId]`.
- Add `updateVideo` mutation:
  - Updates title, description, is_premium, price, and playlist_id.
  - Optionally updates the thumbnail if a new file is provided.

### [Component] CircleVideoCard
#### [MODIFY] [CircleVideoCard.tsx](file:///c:/Users/elink/./.gemini/antigravity/scratch/MomNest/heart-lens-studio-main/src/components/circles/CircleVideoCard.tsx)
- Add `isOwner`, `onEdit`, and `onDelete` props.
- Use `DropdownMenu` to provide "Edit" and "Delete" actions in the top-right corner (visible only if `isOwner`).

### [Component] CircleVideoComposer
#### [MODIFY] [CircleVideoComposer.tsx](file:///c:/Users/elink/./.gemini/antigravity/scratch/MomNest/heart-lens-studio-main/src/components/circles/CircleVideoComposer.tsx)
- Add `videoToEdit?: CircleVideo` prop.
- Populate initial state from `videoToEdit` using `useEffect`.
- Update [handleUpload](file:///c:/Users/elink/.gemini/antigravity/scratch/MomNest/heart-lens-studio-main/src/components/circles/CircleVideoComposer.tsx#53-75) to call `updateVideo` mutation if editing.

### [Component] CircleVideos
#### [MODIFY] [CircleVideos.tsx](file:///c:/Users/elink/./.gemini/antigravity/scratch/MomNest/heart-lens-studio-main/src/components/circles/CircleVideos.tsx)
- Add `editingVideo` state.
- Pass `isOwner`, `onEdit`, and `onDelete` to [CircleVideoCard](file:///c:/Users/elink/.gemini/antigravity/scratch/MomNest/heart-lens-studio-main/src/components/circles/CircleVideoCard.tsx#13-99).
- Implement `handleDelete` with an `AlertDialog` confirmation.
- Open [CircleVideoComposer](file:///c:/Users/elink/.gemini/antigravity/scratch/MomNest/heart-lens-studio-main/src/components/circles/CircleVideoComposer.tsx#19-294) in edit mode when `onEdit` is triggered.

## Verification Plan

### Manual Verification
1.  **Delete Video**:
    - Tap the "More" menu on a video card.
    - Select "Delete".
    - Confirm in the dialog.
    - Verify the video disappears from the list and a success toast appears.
2.  **Edit Video**:
    - Tap "Edit" in the "More" menu.
    - Verify the composer opens with existing video details (title, description, etc.).
    - Change the title and save.
    - Verify the card updates with the new title.
